                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Olney</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Williams</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-05-02"><hi rend="italic">May 2,
                                1896</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>Yours of yesterday respecting <hi rend="italic">Competitor</hi>
                            passengers received and acted upon. What is situation to-day? Cable.</p>
